  "slug": "slice",
  "title": "Slice - Radial hotbar",
  "description": "Turns your hotbar into a customizable radial menu.",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n    <img alt=\"Slice Icon\" title=\"Slice\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fc3a60516f4b9a25606c4bed70256fcda3018290.png\" width=\"512\">\n</p>\n\n<br>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/slice/versions?l=neoforge\"><img alt=\"neoforge\" src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/8494ec1ac495cfb481dc7e458356325510933eb0/assets/cozy/supported/neoforge_vector.svg?raw=true\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/slice/versions?l=forge\"><img alt=\"forge\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/forge_vector.svg\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/slice/versions?l=fabric\"><img alt=\"forge\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/fabric_vector.svg\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/slice/versions?l=quilt\"><img alt=\"forge\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/quilt_vector.svg\"></a>\n</p>\n\n## Features\n- Flexible layout control with adjustable radius, item size, and rotation angles\n- Visibility options for slots, numbers, and sprites\n- Multiple interaction modes (toggle menu or click-to-select item)\n- Configurable inner and outer deadzones\n- Hotbar scrolling toggle\n- Custom texture pack support\n\n## Screenshots\n\n![alt text](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ansi-sudo/Slice/HEAD/.github/InGame1.png)\n[Click to watch the trailer/demo](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kq3pwFCv4ZM)\n\n## Supported Versions\n> ✅ - Supported, ❌ - Unsupported, 🔍 - Planned / In development\n\n<table>\n    <th>Version</th>\n    <th></th>\n    <th>Loaders</th>\n    <th>Minimum required version</th>\n    <th>Latest Slice version</th>\n    <tr><td>26.1.2</td>  <td>✅</td>\n        <td>\n          <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/8494ec1ac495cfb481dc7e458356325510933eb0/assets/cozy-minimal/supported/neoforge_vector.svg?raw=true\"> \n          <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://badges.penpow.dev/badges/supported/forge/cozy-minimal.svg\"> \n          <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://badges.penpow.dev/badges/supported/fabric/cozy-minimal.svg\">\n        </td>\n        <td><code>26.1.2.0-beta</code>, <code>64.0.0</code>, <code>0.18.4</code></td>\n        <td><code>1.0.2</code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td>26.1.1</td>  <td>✅</td>\n        <td>\n          <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/8494ec1ac495cfb481dc7e458356325510933eb0/assets/cozy-minimal/supported/neoforge_vector.svg?raw=true\"> \n          <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://badges.penpow.dev/badges/supported/forge/cozy-minimal.svg\"> \n          <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://badges.penpow.dev/badges/supported/fabric/cozy-minimal.svg\">\n        </td>\n        <td><code>26.1.1.0-beta</code>, <code>63.0.1</code>, <code>0.18.4</code></td>\n        <td><code>1.0.2</code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td>26.1</td> <td>✅</td>\n        <td>\n            <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/8494ec1ac495cfb481dc7e458356325510933eb0/assets/cozy-minimal/supported/neoforge_vector.svg?raw=true\"> \n            <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://badges.penpow.dev/badges/supported/fabric/cozy-minimal.svg\">\n        </td>\n        <td><code>26.1.0.1-beta</code>, <code>0.18.4</code></td>\n        <td><code>1.0.1</code></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td>1.21.11</td>  <td>✅</td>\n        <td>\n          <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/8494ec1ac495cfb481dc7e458356325510933eb0/assets/cozy-minimal/supported/neoforge_vector.svg?raw=true\"> \n          <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://badges.penpow.dev/badges/supported/forge/cozy-minimal.svg\"> \n          <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://badges.penpow.dev/badges/supported/fabric/cozy-minimal.svg\">\n          <img width=\"35\" src=\"https://badges.penpow.dev/badges